com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce

Class MapReduceSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.MapSettings
      • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.MapReduceSettings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MapReduceSettings
extends MapSettings
    Settings that affect how a MapReduce is executed. May affect performance and resource usage, but should not affect the result (unless the result is dependent on the performance or resource usage of the computation, or if different backends, modules or different base urls have different versions of the code).
